## Project Configuration

This project contains 2 spiders:

1. **`conso_outlet_finder`** — geo-grid based restaurant discovery
2. **`conso_outlet_detail`** — restaurant detail + menu collection

### Spider Parameters (`-a` arguments)

#### `conso_outlet_finder` args:

| Parameter | Required | Default | Description |
|:----------|:---------|:--------|:------------|
| `prefix` | Yes | — | 2-char country code (e.g. `US`) |
| `grid_name` | No | same as `prefix` | Redis key suffix override |
| `local_test` | No | `False` | Use test Redis; skip prod writes |
| `sample` | No | `0` | Close spider after N items (`0` = production) |

#### `conso_outlet_detail` args:

| Parameter | Required | Default | Description |
|:----------|:---------|:--------|:------------|
| `prefix` | Yes | — | 2-char country code (e.g. `US`) |
| `output_month` | Yes | — | S3 partition month in `YYYYMM` format |
| `recrawl` | No | `True` | Re-crawl already-seen outlets |
| `id_refresh` | No | `True` | Refresh Redis queue from MySQL |
| `local_test` | No | `False` | Use test Redis and `s3://dash-alpha-dev` |
| `sample` | No | `0` | Close spider after N items (`0` = production) |

