## Data Schema

### Output Items

| Table | Stored In | Key Fields |
|-------|-----------|------------|
| `outlets` | MySQL (RDS Pipeline) | `id_outlet`, `country` |
| `outlet_information` | S3 Parquet | `id_outlet`, `name`, `address`, `lat`, `lon`, `rating`, `cuisine`, `opening_hours` |
| `outlet_meal` | S3 Parquet | `id_outlet`, `id_meal`, `id_category`, `name`, `price`, `sold_out` |
| `meal_option` | S3 Parquet | `id_outlet`, `id_option`, `name`, `price` |

> Tables collected by this platform: `outlet_information`, `outlet_meal`, `meal_option`

### Supported Countries

| Prefix | Country |
|--------|---------|
| US | United States |
| CA | Canada |
